rawReviews.name: Paxton Parker
rawReviews.text: This is my first and only Google review. I'm sure it'll get buried by the other fake reviews from friends, family, and worst of all, employees, but I feel it's necessary in order to expose the harsh truths about this company. I originally chose them due to their professional online appearance and responsiveness on the front end, but quickly found it to be a complete facade. After 3 separate reschedule requests from this company, each made hours before our scheduled septic pump & inspection, we agreed to meet at 8:00 am 8/27/20 (the following morning) to complete the service. After arriving at the agreed upon address, at the agreed upon time, the seller of our future house and I, waited for 1 hour and 15 minutes for them to show before finally giving up. Several attempts were made to contact both the "dispatcher" and technician, with every call being sent straight to voicemail. It's now 10:32 AM, 2 hours and 33 minutes past our appointment time and I've yet to receive any attempts of communication, be it an explanation or apology. Don't let these guys deceive you like they did me. Choose a company that can give you a specific timeline and stick to it.
rawReviews.title: Affordable Septic LLC
